(46, 'Lucy', '<p>[Куплет 1]<br>Hey, Lucy, I remember your name<br>I left a dozen roses on your grave today<br>I\'m in the grass on my knees, wipe the leaves away<br>I just came to talk for a while<br>I got some things I need to say<br><br>[Припев]<br>Now that it\'s over<br>I just want to hold her<br>I\'d give up all the world to see<br>That little piece of Heaven lookin\' back at me<br>Now that it\'s over<br>I just want to hold her<br>I\'ve got to live with the choices I made<br>And I can\'t live with myself today<br><br>[Куплет 2]<br>Hey Lucy, I remembered your birthday<br>They said it\'d bring some closure to say your name<br>I know I\'d do it all different if I had the chance<br>But all I got are these roses to give<br>And they can\'t help me make amends<br><br>[Припев]<br>Now that it\'s over<br>I just want to hold her<br>I\'d give up all the world to see<br>That little piece of Heaven lookin\' back at me<br>Now that it\'s over<br>I just want to hold her<br>I\'ve got to live with the choices I made<br>And I can\'t live with myself today</p><p>[Бридж]<br>Here we are, now you\'re in my arms<br>I never wanted anything so bad<br>Here we are, for a brand new start<br>Living the life that we could\'ve had<br><br>[Куплет 3]<br>Me and Lucy walkin\' hand in hand<br>Me and Lucy never want to end<br>Just another moment in your eyes<br>I\'ll see you in another life<br>In Heaven where we never say goodbye<br><br>[Припев]<br>Now that it\'s over<br>I just want to hold her<br>I\'d give up all the world to see<br>That little piece of Heaven lookin\' back at me<br>Now that it\'s over<br>I just want to hold her<br>I\'ve got to live with the choices I made<br>And I can\'t live with myself today<br><br>[Куплет 4]<br>Here we are, now you\'re in my arms<br>Here we are for a brand new start<br>Got to live with the choices I\'ve made<br>And I can\'t live with myself today<br>Me and Lucy walking hand in hand<br>Me and Lucy never want to end<br>Got to live with the choices I\'ve made<br>And I can\'t live with myself today<br><br>[Заключение]<br>Hey, Lucy, I remember your name</p>', 7, '<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WIHbxrI5TCk\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<iframe frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:none;width:100%;height:180px;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://music.yandex.ru/iframe/#track/418013/43233\">Слушайте <a href=\'https://music.yandex.ru/album/43233/track/418013\'>Lucy</a> — <a href=\'https://music.yandex.ru/artist/49258\'>Skillet</a> на Яндекс.Музыке</iframe>'),
(47, 'Dead inside', '<p>[Куплет 1]<br>To find this love of mine<br>I’d walk through wind and fire<br>Forever and always<br>These hollow hands reach out<br>For you to touch me now<br>Forever and always<br><br>Dead inside<br>My heart and soul flatlines<br>Put your mouth on mine<br>And bring me back to life<br>Dead inside<br>No other satisfies<br>My blood runs dry<br>Take my life<br>Save me from this death inside<br><br>I can’t escape this love<br>I want it the way it was<br>Forever and always<br>Don’t you leave me here<br>Alone in all this fear<br>Forever and always<br><br>[Припев]<br>Dead inside<br>My heart and soul flatlines<br>Put your mouth on mine<br>And bring me back to life<br>Dead inside<br>No other satisfies<br>My blood runs dry<br>Take my life<br>Save me from this death inside<br><br>[Припев]<br>I can’t escape this love<br>I want it the way it was<br>You remind me of a time<br>When I felt alive<br><br>Dead inside<br>My heart and soul flatlines<br>Put your mouth on mine<br>And bring me back to life<br>Dead inside<br>No other satisfies<br>My blood runs dry<br>Take my life<br>Save me from this death inside<br>My blood runs dry<br>Take my life<br>Save me from this death inside</p>', 7, '<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/64xckMd0l34\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<iframe frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:none;width:100%;height:180px;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://music.yandex.ru/iframe/#track/418020/43233\">Слушайте <a href=\'https://music.yandex.ru/album/43233/track/418020\'>Dead Inside</a> — <a href=\'https://music.yandex.ru/artist/49258\'>Skillet</a> на Яндекс.Музыке</iframe>'),
(48, 'Would it matter', '<p>[Куплет 1]<br>If I wasn\'t here tomorrow<br>Would anybody care?<br>If my time was up I\'d wanna know<br>You were happy I was there<br>If I wasn\'t here tomorrow<br>Would anyone lose sleep?<br>If I wasn\'t hard and hollow<br>Then maybe you would miss me<br><br>[Припев]<br>I know I\'m a mess and I wanna be someone<br>Someone that I like better<br>I can never forget<br>So don\'t remind me of it forever<br>(Forever)<br><br>[Припев]<br>What if I just pulled myself together?<br>Would it matter at all?<br>What if I just tried not to remember?<br>Would it matter at all?<br>All the chances that have passed me by<br>Would it matter if I gave it one more try?<br>Would it matter at all?<br><br>[Куплет 2]<br>If I wasn\'t here tomorrow<br>Would anybody care?<br>Still stuck inside this sorrow<br>I\'ve got nothin\' and goin\' nowhere<br><br>[Пред-припев]<br>I know I\'m a mess and I wanna be someone<br>Someone that I like better<br>I can never forget<br>So don\'t remind me of it forever<br><br>[Припев]<br>What if I just pulled myself together?<br>Would it matter at all?<br>What if I just tried not to remember?<br>Would it matter at all?<br>All the chances that have passed me by<br>Would it matter if I gave it one more try?<br>Would it matter at all?<br><br>[Пред-припев]<br>I know I\'m a mess and I wanna be someone<br>Someone that I like better<br>Can you help me forget?<br>Don\'t wanna feel like this forever<br>Forever!<br><br>[Припев]<br>What if I just pulled myself together?<br>Would it matter at all?<br>What if I just tried not to remember?<br>Would it matter at all?<br>All the chances that have passed me by<br>Would it matter if I gave it one more try?<br>Would it matter at all?<br><br>[Бридж]<br>If I left tomorrow<br>Would anybody care?<br>Stuck in this sorrow<br>Going nowhere<br><br>[Заключение]<br>All the chances that have passed me by<br>Would it matter if I gave it one more try?<br>Would it matter at all?</p>', 7, '<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"