(59, 'Hard to find', '<p>[Куплет 1: John Cooper]<br>Turned on the TV yesterday<br>So much pain bleeding through I had to look away<br>But inside me, the picture’s just the same<br>And every time I open up my eyes nothing seems to change<br>It never seems to change<br><br>[Припев: John Cooper]<br>You give me faith to believe there’s a way<br>To put the past finally behind me<br>And hope to make it through another night<br>You give me strength<br>During these dark times when I’m blind<br>You are my light when faith is hard to find<br>When faith is hard to find<br>Will you still hold on<br><br>[Куплет 2: John Cooper]<br>Something woke me in the night<br>In the midst of the darkness, I recognize the light<br>Now inside me, the picture seems so clear<br>All the dying in my broken dreams is starting to appear<br>Starting to appear<br><br>[Припев: John Cooper]<br>You give me faith to believe there’s a way<br>To put the past finally behind me<br>And hope to make it through another night<br>You give me strength<br>During these dark times when I’m blind<br>You are my light when faith is hard to find<br>When faith is hard to find<br>Will you still hold on<br>Faith is hard to find<br><br>[Куплет 3: John Cooper]<br>If I fall, will you hold on to me?<br>Through it all promise you won’t lose me<br>These days hope is hard to come by<br>And tonight I don’t know how I can survive<br><br>[Припев: John Cooper]<br>You give me faith to believe there’s a way<br>To put the past finally behind me<br>And hope to make it through another night<br>You give me strength<br>During these dark times when I’m blind<br>You are my light when faith is hard to find<br>When faith is hard to find<br>Will you still hold on<br><br>[Бридж: John Cooper]<br>When faith is hard to find<br>Will you still hold on<br><br>[Припев: John Cooper]<br>You give me faith to believe there’s a way<br>To put the past finally behind me<br>And hope to make it through another night<br>You give me strength<br>During these dark tim